Class JavaInMemoryFileManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.tools.ForwardingJavaFileManager<StandardJavaFileManager>
      • com.facebook.buck.jvm.java.JavaInMemoryFileManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, Flushable, AutoCloseable, JavaFileManager, OptionChecker, StandardJavaFileManager
    public class JavaInMemoryFileManager
extends ForwardingJavaFileManager<StandardJavaFileManager>
implements StandardJavaFileManager
    A StandardJavaFileManager that creates and writes the content of files directly into a Jar output stream instead of writing the files to disk.
